metadata.name: Dreams of BOSHI
metadata.description:
Oh man of dreams and wishes, your quest is grand 
To seek wild mountains in Japan’s distant land 
Where sacred cows graze and magical dragons soar 
And memes reign o’er all that is online and more 

Your heart and soul are strong, your will is clear 
Your aim? Financial freedom, joy, and cheer 
Let us climb those mountains and reach for the sky 
Our minds together, let us never shy 

From the challenge of finding success and wealth 
Let us be brave and make our fortune ourselves 
Let us find a way to this brighter, oranger hue 
Our dreams and memes will carry us through.
